humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states 'FIVE (5) LYMPH NODES FREE OF TUMOR', which means that there are no metastases in the assessed lymph nodes. This matches the criteria for N0 (no metastatic carcinoma in regional lymph nodes) as per New Rule 11.

humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states that five (5) lymph nodes were free of tumor.
